s><trans-unit id="01864fbe-ddb5-4159-b5b7-7ddd58a828bb"><source>Why Is the Battery Energy Insufficient During Morning Peak Hours?</source><seg-source><mrk mtype="seg" mid="1">Why Is the Battery Energy Insufficient During Morning Peak Hours?</mrk></seg-source><target><mrk mtype="seg" mid="1">Why Is the Battery Energy Insufficient During Morning Peak Hours?</mrk></target><sdl:seg-defs><sdl:seg id="1" origin="source"><sdl:value key="SegmentIdentityHash">0YZ3LZS70MmDIqk6sg9iUnHgYgY=</sdl:value></sdl:seg></sdl:seg-defs></trans-unit></group><group><sdl:cxts><sdl:cxt id="1" /><sdl:cxt id="2" /><sdl:cxt id="3" /></sdl:cxts><trans-unit id="246be558-e7b5-42f5-a01c-d3b56e5e21f8"><source>During morning peak hours, electricity demand is high, but PV power generation has not yet reached its peak.</source><seg-source><mrk mtype="seg" mid="2">During morning peak hours, electricity demand is high, but PV power generation has not yet reached its peak.</mrk></seg-source><target><mrk mtype="seg" mid="2">During morning peak hours, electricity demand is high, but PV power generation has not yet reached its peak.</mrk></target><sdl:seg-defs><sdl:seg id="2" origin="source"><sdl:value key="SegmentIdentityHash">HPqwu2s0I48vcwYq8oBwli7+5SI=</sdl:value></sdl:seg></sdl:seg-defs></trans-unit></group><group><sdl:cxts><sdl:cxt id="1" /><sdl:cxt id="2" /><sdl:cxt id="3" /></sdl:cxts><trans-unit id="67257396-4b51-4218-83a6-35fc69acf836"><source>Therefore, the system mainly relies on battery discharge to meet load demand.</source><seg-source><mrk mtype="seg" mid="3">Therefore, the system mainly relies on battery discharge to meet load demand.</mrk></seg-source><target><mrk mtype="seg" mid="3">Therefore, the system mainly relies on battery discharge to meet load demand.</mrk></target><sdl:seg-defs><sdl:seg id="3" origin="source"><sdl:value key="SegmentIdentityHash">2CFwjNpIuENAifrG6P6LTjBydjI=</sdl:value></sdl:seg></sdl:seg-defs></trans-unit></group><group><sdl:cxts><sdl:cxt id="1" /><sdl:cxt id="2" /><sdl:cxt id="3" /></sdl:cxts><trans-unit id="659755aa-61f5-4322-a17c-d73ee6ad4522"><source>Battery policy restrictions</source><seg-source><mrk mtype="seg" mid="4">Battery policy restrictions</mrk></seg-source><target><mrk mtype="seg" mid="4">Battery policy restrictions</mrk></target><sdl:seg-defs><sdl:seg id="4" origin="source"><sdl:value key="SegmentIdentityHash">iJMN+Z5O4IDtJeGm/2I7lnI/LSo=</sdl:value></sdl:seg></sdl:seg-defs></trans-unit></group><group><sdl:cxts><sdl:cxt id="1" /><sdl:cxt id="2" /><sdl:cxt id="3" /></sdl:cxts><trans-unit id="676d4a39-5149-483f-9acb-49cfa337ff61"><source><g id="3">Incorrect <x id="1" /> period settings</g>:</source><seg-source><mrk mtype="seg" mid="5"><g id="3">Incorrect <x id="1" /> period settings</g>:</mrk></seg-source><target><mrk mtype="seg" mid="5"><g id="3">Incorrect <x id="1" /> period settings</g>:</mrk></target><sdl:seg-defs><sdl:seg id="5" origin="source"><sdl:value key="SegmentIdentityHash">jZCiIPRIzfTxkBfrcMjydSV+P+I=</sdl:value></sdl:seg></sdl:seg-defs></trans-unit></group><group><sdl:cxts><sdl:cxt id="1" /><sdl:cxt id="2" /><sdl:cxt id="3" /></sdl:cxts><trans-unit id="0ebb45c9-4e29-4cc0-90f0-6c58f897aa02"><source>If the charging window is not set for nighttime (low electricity price period), the system does not fully charge the battery at night or during low electricity price periods.</source><seg-source><mrk mtype="seg" mid="6">If the charging window is not set for nighttime (low electricity price period), the system does not fully charge the battery at night or during low electricity price periods.</mrk></seg-source><target><mrk mtype="seg" mid="6">If the charging window is not set for nighttime (low electricity price period), the system does not fully charge the battery at night or during low electricity price periods.</mrk></target><sdl:seg-defs><sdl:seg id="6" origin="source"><sdl:value key="SegmentIdentityHash">SD2cbbJtbAinjnA2rcQ21uiSB+Y=</sdl:value></sdl:seg></sdl:seg-defs></trans-unit></group><group><sdl:cxts><sdl:cxt id="1" /><sdl:cxt id="2" /><sdl:cxt id="3" /></sdl:cxts><trans-unit id="62ef81e9-f3d8-4bc9-b1cf-ce4745363a04"><source>Consequently, the battery's energy reserve is insufficient during peak morning hours.</source><seg-source><mrk mtype="seg" mid="7">Consequently, the battery's energy reserve is insufficient during peak morning hours.</mrk></seg-source><target><mrk mtype="seg" mid="7">Consequently, the battery's energy reserve is insufficient during peak morning hours.</mrk></target><sdl:seg-defs><sdl:seg id="7" origin="source"><sdl:value key="SegmentIdentityHash">vl0Z3TDe5K/oZR5/f3XdVYcLRCI=</sdl:value></sdl:seg></sdl:seg-defs></trans-unit></group><group><sdl:cxts><sdl:cxt id="1" /><sdl:cxt id="2" /><sdl:cxt id="3" /></sdl:cxts><trans-unit id="57ad714f-de10-4874-a1a9-61adba2f5424"><source><g id="6">Conservative SOC threshold setting</g>:</source><seg-source><mrk mtype="seg" mid="8"><g id="6">Conservative SOC threshold setting</g>:</mrk></seg-source><target><mrk mtype="seg" mid="8"><g id="6">Conservative SOC threshold setting</g>:</mrk></target><sdl:seg-defs><sdl:seg id="8" origin="source"><sdl:value key="SegmentIdentityHash">+WqNPhr8gtOdLdHwd/P9gbwSx5g=</sdl:value></sdl:seg></sdl:seg-defs></trans-unit></group><group><sdl:cxts><sdl:cxt id="1" /><sdl:cxt id="2" /><sdl:cxt id="3" /></sdl:cxts><trans-unit id="92bcf422-c44d-40f5-a992-398e0d89dd67"><source>If the end-of-discharge SOC is set too high (for example, 50%), the available capacity decreases.</source><seg-source><mrk mtype="seg" mid="9">If the end-of-discharge SOC is set too high (for example, 50%), the available capacity decreases.</mrk></seg-source><target><mrk mtype="seg" mid="9">If the end-of-discharge SOC is set too high (for example, 50%), the available capacity decreases.</mrk></target><sdl:seg-defs><sdl:seg id="9" origin="source"><sdl:value key="SegmentIdentityHash">NeKvZTnZsYsVNLZP0SruwjsK17g=</sdl:value></sdl:seg></sdl:seg-defs></trans-unit></group><group><sdl:cxts><sdl:cxt id="1" /><sdl:cxt id="2" /><sdl:cxt id="3" /></sdl:cxts><trans-unit id="ceb1e327-9cfc-44a7-8d0c-0f666af8f766"><source>Consequently, the battery's energy is depleted earlier than expected during peak hours.</source><seg-source><mrk mtype="seg" mid="10">Consequently, the battery's energy is depleted earlier than expected during peak hours.</mrk></seg-source><target><mrk mtype="seg" mid="10">Consequently, the battery's energy is depleted earlier than expected during peak hours.</mrk></target><sdl:seg-defs><sdl:seg id="10" origin="source"><sdl:value key="SegmentIdentityHash">WRJxfBcOfeJ+KaBzK+CSZU7AaBU=</sdl:value></sdl:seg></sdl:seg-defs></trans-unit></group><group><sdl:cxts><sdl:cxt id="1" /><sdl:cxt id="2" /><sdl:cxt id="3" /></sdl:cxts><trans-unit id="ed497a66-3ac6-48c1-8003-ee6e8f6e98cd"><source><g id="9">Feed-in priority mode</g>:</source><seg-source><mrk mtype="seg" mid="11"><g id="9">Feed-in priority mode</g>:</mrk></seg-source><target><mrk mtype="seg" mid="11"><g id="9">Feed-in priority mode</g>:</mrk></target><sdl:seg-defs><sdl:seg id="11" origin="source"><sdl:value key="SegmentIdentityHash">M9HYyTd3IrEj3HEJjw+RfEneMSI=</sdl:value></sdl:seg></sdl:seg-defs></trans-unit></group><group><sdl:cxts><sdl:cxt id="1" /><sdl:cxt id="2" /><sdl:cxt id="3" /></sdl:cxts><trans-unit id="cd7332fe-d33a-4d5b-8717-f5a57d69ac69"><source>If the mode is set to <x id="10" />, PV power is used first to meet home load requirements, and the remaining power is directly sold, affecting the battery's energy reserve.</source><seg-source><mrk mtype="seg" mid="12">If the mode is set to <x id="10" />, PV power is used first to meet home load requirements, and the remaining power is directly sold, affecting the battery's energy reserve.</mrk></seg-source><target><mrk mtype="seg" mid="12">If the mode is set to <x id="10" />, PV power is used first to meet home load requirements, and the remaining power is directly sold, affecting the battery's energy reserve.</mrk></target><sdl:seg-defs><sdl:seg id="12" origin="source"><sdl:value key="SegmentIdentityHash">zDq62hD9mYxNhRCLq7bMGe34u4I=</sdl:value></sdl:seg></sdl:seg-defs></trans-unit></group><group><sdl:cxts><sdl:cxt id="1" /><sdl:cxt id="2" /><sdl:cxt id="3" /></sdl:cxts><trans-unit id="99bf196d-4684-4595-a4d2-38f1b0a357f3"><source>Battery capacity and power limits</source><seg-source><mrk mtype="seg" mid="13">Battery capacity and power limits</mrk></seg-source><target><mrk mtype="seg" mid="13">Battery capacity and power limits</mrk></target><sdl:seg-defs><sdl:seg id="13" origin="source"><sdl:value key="SegmentIdentityHash">c3M+bLvvcx5bmebilzfU/yd7Jjg=</sdl:value></sdl:seg></sdl:seg-defs></trans-unit></group><group><sdl:cxts><sdl:cxt id="1" /><sdl:cxt id="2" /><sdl:cxt id="3" /></sdl:cxts><trans-unit id="e7172896-805f-4399-90cd-59112307213b"><source><g id="13">Insufficient capacity</g>:</source><seg-source><mrk mtype="seg" mid="14"><g id="13">Insufficient capacity</g>:</mrk></seg-source><target><mrk mtype="seg" mid="14">Onvoldoende capaciteit</mrk></target><sdl:seg-defs><sdl:seg id="14"><sdl:value key="SegmentIdentityHash">zK53PK/KIh+Xfn94Y4qgVYkxlL8=</sdl:value></sdl:seg></sdl:seg-defs></trans-unit></group><group><sdl:cxts><sdl:cxt id="1" /><sdl:cxt id="2" /><sdl:cxt id="3" /></sdl:cxts><trans-unit id="b6ba6ea5-416d-4879-9d95-0997eb32aa5c"><source>If the total battery capacity (kWh) cannot meet the load demand during peak hours, the energy will be quickly depleted.</source><seg-source><mrk mtype="seg" mid="15">If the total battery capacity (kWh) cannot meet the load demand during peak hours, the energy will be quickly depleted.</mrk></seg-source><target><mrk mtype="seg" mid="15">If the total battery capacity (kWh) cannot meet the load demand during peak hours, the energy will be quickly depleted.</mrk></target><sdl:seg-defs><sdl:seg id="15" origin="source"><sdl:value key="SegmentIdentityHash">SFxQPAjKbpFLRHVwL/kId+KiFD0=</sdl:value></sdl:seg></sdl:seg-defs></trans-unit></group><group><sdl:cxts><sdl:cxt id="1" /><sdl:cxt id="2" /><sdl:cxt id="3" /></sdl:cxts><trans-unit id="b7b26b64-5657-4f7f-b2da-c156e4e8d4e7"><source>For example, if the load is 5 kW for 4 hours during morning peak hours, at least 20 kWh of capacity is required.</source><seg-source><mrk mtype="seg" mid="16">For example, if the load is 5 kW for 4 hours during morning peak hours, at least 20 kWh of capacity is required.</mrk></seg-source><target><mrk mtype="seg" mid="16">For example, if the load is 5 kW for 4 hours during morning peak hours, at least 20 kWh of capacity is required.</mrk></target><sdl:seg-defs><sdl:seg id="16" origin="source"><sdl:value key="SegmentIdentityHash">2PaaJ3ShGBInfY//haFndkG5xZg=</sdl:value></sdl:seg></sdl:seg-defs></trans-unit></group><group><sdl:cxts><sdl:cxt id="1" /><sdl:cxt id="2" /><sdl:cxt id="3" /></sdl:cxts><trans-unit id="220efe98-2735-4094-8fc5-bceca7f0ba8f"><source>If the battery capacity is only 10 kWh, it is insufficient.</source><seg-source><mrk mtype="seg" mid="17">If the battery capacity is only 10 kWh, it is insufficient.</mrk></seg-source><target><mrk mtype="seg" mid="17">If the battery capacity is only 10 kWh, it is insufficient.</mrk></target><sdl:seg-defs><sdl:seg id="17" origin="source"><sdl:value key="SegmentIdentityHash">ENDuL1mn2eivjX5+2aJ0ikvUMZk=</sdl:value></sdl:seg></sdl:seg-defs></trans-unit></group><group><sdl:cxts><sdl:cxt id="1" /><sdl:cxt id="2" /><sdl:cxt id="3" /></sdl:cxts><trans-unit id="25836996-fb5b-4be3-a417-c17acb55a2f4"><source><g id="16">Insufficient power</g>:</source><seg-source><mrk mtype="seg" mid="18"><g id="16">Insufficient power</g>:</mrk></seg-source><target><mrk mtype="seg" mid="18">Onvoldoende groene stroom</mrk></target><sdl:seg-defs><sdl:seg id="18"><sdl:value key="SegmentIdentityHash">MWu2FvwsVm/DDzve2C4CT+9fHyg=</sdl:value></sdl:seg></sdl:seg-defs></trans-unit></group><group><sdl:cxts><sdl:cxt id="1" /><sdl:cxt id="2" /><sdl:cxt id="3" /></sdl:cxts><trans-unit id="a60e5c8e-e0ec-411d-bf21-0bcc230de432"><source>If the maximum discharge power (kW) of the battery is lower than the peak load, the system cannot support devices with sudden high-power demands (such as air conditioners starting simultaneously).</source><seg-source><mrk mtype="seg" mid="19">If the maximum discharge power (kW) of the battery is lower than the peak load, the system cannot support devices with sudden high-power demands (such as air conditioners starting simultaneously).</mrk></seg-source><target><mrk mtype="seg" mid="19">If the maximum discharge power (kW) of the battery is lower than the peak load, the system cannot support devices with sudden high-power demands (such as air conditioners starting simultaneously).</mrk></target><sdl:seg-defs><sdl:seg id="19" origin="source"><sdl:value key="SegmentIdentityHash">txZhd1JFmMfS0EPiMKEv8YaaOSc=</sdl:value></sdl:seg></sdl:seg-defs></trans-unit></group><group><sdl:cxts><sdl:cxt id="1" /><sdl:cxt id="2" /><sdl:cxt id="3" /></sdl:cxts><trans-unit id="5840a6fe-f63e-4128-b208-003f634cec45"><source>Load fluctuation and prediction deviation</source><seg-source><mrk mtype="seg" mid="20">Load fluctuation and prediction deviation</mrk></seg-source><target><mrk mtype="seg" mid="20">Load fluctuation and prediction deviation</mrk></target><sdl:seg-defs><sdl:seg id="20" origin="source"><sdl:rep id="UlgMQUJVYheYeLMjTLfrCGraZjw=" /><sdl:value key="SegmentIdentityHash">UlgMQUJVYheYeLMjTLfrCGraZjw=</sdl:value></sdl:seg></sdl:seg-defs></trans-unit></group><group><sdl:cxts><sdl:cxt id="1" /><sdl:cxt id="2" /><sdl:cxt id="3" /></sdl:cxts><trans-unit id="0f991183-6b33-40af-9890-89ca734a3718"><source><g id="19">Sudden load peak</g>:</source><seg-source><mrk mtype="seg" mid="21"><g id="19">Sudden load peak</g>:</mrk></seg-source><target><mrk mtype="seg" mid="21"><g id="19">Sudden load peak</g>:</mrk></target><sdl:seg-defs><sdl:seg id="21" origin="source"><sdl:rep id="hERLd8J/p9tsdgErRcX1lqWLPGE=" /><sdl:value key="SegmentIdentityHash">hERLd8J/p9tsdgErRcX1lqWLPGE=</sdl:value></sdl:seg></sdl:seg-defs></trans-unit></group><group><sdl:cxts><sdl:cxt id="1" /><sdl:cxt id="2" /><sdl:cxt id="3" /></sdl:cxts><trans-unit id="92cffb6a-bc76-4883-8de1-8a10c28f27e8"><source>During morning and evening peak hours, home electricity consumption is concentrated (such as cooking and charging).</source><seg-source><mrk mtype="seg" mid="22">During morning and evening peak hours, home electricity consumption is concentrated (such as cooking and charging).</mrk></seg-source><target><mrk mtype="seg" mid="22">During morning and evening peak hours, home electricity consumption is concentrated (such as cooking and charging).</mrk></target><sdl:seg-defs><sdl:seg id="22" origin="source"><sdl:rep id="jt3ny+wH4ubkiLD6/PbF6R/8BVI=" /><sdl:value key="SegmentIdentityHash">jt3ny+wH4ubkiLD6/PbF6R/8BVI=</sdl:value></sdl:seg></sdl:seg-defs></trans-unit></group><group><sdl:cxts><sdl:cxt id="1" /><sdl:cxt id="2" /><sdl:cxt id="3" /></sdl:cxts><trans-unit id="b0d5590a-fcf4-4597-aaf6-f75a245c7171"><source>If the load suddenly increases beyond the predicted range, the battery may not be able to respond.</source><seg-source><mrk mtype="seg" mid="23">If the load suddenly increases beyond the predicted range, the battery may not be able to respond.</mrk></seg-source><target><mrk mtype="seg" mid="23">If the load suddenly increases beyond the predicted range, the battery may not be able to respond.</mrk></target><sdl:seg-defs><sdl:seg id="23" origin="source"><sdl:rep id="Ln2bUWyRqa8jE8WwTGgeCT7q0Co=" /><sdl:value key="SegmentIdentityHash">Ln2bUWyRqa8jE8WwTGgeCT7q0Co=</sdl:value></sdl:seg></sdl:seg-defs></trans-unit></group><group><sdl:cxts><sdl:cxt id="1" /><sdl:cxt id="2" /><sdl:cxt id="3" /></sdl:cxts><trans-unit id="d6d4cda2-5abe-4d9e-8637-4390f5723fa4"><source><g id="22">Prediction algorithm error</g>:</source><seg-source><mrk mtype="seg" mid="24"><g id="22">Prediction algorithm error</g>:</mrk></seg-source><target><mrk mtype="seg" mid="24"><g id="22">Prediction algorithm error</g>:</mrk></target><sdl:seg-defs><sdl:seg id="24" origin="source"><sdl:rep id="THGAC3uydOeQGjK7BPOYiAdjZl4=" /><sdl:value key="SegmentIdentityHash">THGAC3uydOeQGjK7BPOYiAdjZl4=</sdl:value></sdl:seg></sdl:seg-defs></trans-unit></group><group><sdl:cxts><sdl:cxt id="1" /><sdl:cxt id="2" /><sdl:cxt id="3" /></sdl:cxts><trans-unit id="5cb05fac-e6d2-4e26-94c5-b21fad2360ea"><source>The system schedules energy based on historical electricity consumption data.</source><seg-source><mrk mtype="seg" mid="25">The system schedules energy based on historical electricity consumption data.</mrk></seg-source><target><mrk mtype="seg" mid="25">The system schedules energy based on historical electricity consumption data.</mrk></target><sdl:seg-defs><sdl:seg id="25" origin="source"><sdl:rep id="OnrVaZZyFX/4mMO/8L4112AWnqI=" /><sdl:value key="SegmentIdentityHash">OnrVaZZyFX/4mMO/8L4112AWnqI=</sdl:value></sdl:seg></sdl:seg-defs></trans-unit></group><group><sdl:cxts><sdl:cxt id="1" /><sdl:cxt id="2" /><sdl:cxt id="3" /></sdl:cxts><trans-unit id="374ea76c-20b1-4455-813b-fc2674cf953c"><source>If the actual electricity consumption pattern changes (for example, high-energy-consuming devices are added), the battery's energy reserve may be insufficient.</source><seg-source><mrk mtype="seg" mid="26">If the actual electricity consumption pattern changes (for example, high-energy-consuming devices are added), the battery's energy reserve may be insufficient.</mrk></seg-source><target><mrk mtype="seg" mid="26">If the actual electricity consumption pattern changes (for example, high-energy-consuming devices are added), the battery's energy reserve may be insufficient.</mrk></target><sdl:seg-defs><sdl:seg id="26" origin="source"><sdl:rep id="wUAI31mRhu8Xo/FnbYyAc90k5Nk=" /><sdl:value key="SegmentIdentityHash">wUAI31mRhu8Xo/FnbYyAc90k5Nk=</sdl:value></sdl:seg></sdl:seg-defs></trans-unit></group></body></file></xliff>